imdb.plot outline: Guaranteed to pull at your heartstrings, these inspiring pet adoption stories give you a look inside the Pasadena Humane Society. Meet the adorable adoptable animals and the big-hearted volunteers and staff who work endlessly to find them a perfect forever home. Also, find tips for taking care of your pet, and watch amazingly inspiring rescue stories that will make you feel empowered to help animals in need.
